{"id":32198,"type":3,"name":"Mysterious Eyes","name_cn":"","date":"2000-03-29","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/08/29/32198_jp.jpg","rating":{"rank":2000,"total":21,"count":{"1":0,"2":0,"3":0,"4":0,"5":1,"6":1,"7":3,"8":13,"9":3,"10":0},"score":7.8},"summary":"柯南 OP 07  第168話 - 第204話（計37話）\r\n《Mysterious Eyes》为GARNET CROW的第一张单曲。2000年3月29日由GIZA studio发售\r\n此曲2000年3月29日发售，作词为AZUKI七，作曲为中村由利、编曲为古井弘人。\r\n\r\n因为与单曲《不停行走直到你家》同时发售，在较大的初次亮相方面集聚了许多说法。《不停行走直到你家》和第三张单曲《二人的火箭》、一起收录在了Indies Album《first kaleidscope 〜君の家に着くまでずっと走ってゆく〜》中（“不停行走直到你家”的排版有差异），《Mysterious Eyes》则为完全的伴奏曲。\r\n\r\n从初次亮相前，为动画《名侦探柯南》演唱歌曲成为焦点，也在公信榜排行内达到在榜10周以上的记录。在单曲的销量上，为第十张单曲《梦醒之后》此曲之后的第二位。而且在为《名侦探柯南》演唱的8首歌曲中，作为片头曲使用的为，此曲《Mysterious Eyes》、《泪之往昔》、《As the Dew》和《Misty Mystery》4首歌曲。\r\n\r\n在初回Press盘中装入了《名侦探柯南》插卡游戏的原始插卡。 在《名侦探柯南》的片头曲开头歌手名表示为片假名的“ガーネットクロウ”。","info":"<li><span>艺术家: </span><a href=\"/person/9957\">GARNET CROW</a></li><li><span>厂牌: </span><a href=\"/person/13308\">GIZA studio</a></li><li><span>录音: </span><a href=\"/person/13308\">GIZA studio</a></li><li><span>版本特性: </span>Maxi</li><li><span>发售日期: </span>2000-03-29</li><li><span>价格: </span>￥ 1,050</li><li><span>播放时长: </span>13 m</li><li><span>发行商: </span>GIZA studio</li>","collection":{"on_hold":0,"dropped":0,"wish":0,"collect":27,"doing":2},"tags":[{"name":"GARNET_CROW","count":4},{"name":"OP","count":4},{"name":"名探偵コナン","count":4},{"name":"2000","count":3},{"name":"anime","count":3},{"name":"single","count":3},{"name":"名侦探柯南","count":3},{"name":"GARNET.CROW","count":1},{"name":"＊＊＊","count":1},{"name":"动漫主题曲","count":1},{"name":"单曲","count":1}],"eps":[{"id":144655,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/144655","type":0,"sort":1,"name":"Mysterious Eyes","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":""},{"id":144656,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/144656","type":0,"sort":2,"name":"Timing","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":""},{"id":144657,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/144657","type":0,"sort":3,"name":"Mysterious Eyes (instrumental)","duration":"","airdate":"","commen